---
description: Docs, tests, and small files — keep responses minimal
globs: ["**/*.md", "**/*.test.*", "**/*.spec.*", "**/docs/**"]
alwaysApply: false
---

- One-liner suggestions preferred.
- Do not suggest structural refactors.
- For tests: add the simplest passing test, don't redesign the suite.
- For docs: match existing tone and length.
